	  the MalformedTagState more replaceable, so that handling of
	  unexpected '<' can be intercepted.
	* MonoDevelop.Xml.StateEngine/XmlCDataState.cs,
	  MonoDevelop.Xml.StateEngine/XmlProcessingInstructionState.cs:
	  Tidying up.

