	  MonoDevelop.XmlEditor/XslOutputViewContent.cs,
	  MonoDevelop.XmlEditor/XmlSchemasPanelWidget.cs,
	  MonoDevelop.XmlEditor/XmlEditorListWindow.cs: No longer needed.
